# Lock our docs and Python tooling to LF.
# core.autocrlf=true would otherwise flip the working tree to CRLF, so every
# generator rerun (which writes LF) showed up as mass CRLF<->LF phantom diffs.
# The SWAT+ source lives in a submodule and is unaffected here.
docs/**       text eol=lf
*.py          text eol=lf
README.md     text eol=lf
AGENTS.md     text eol=lf
